Tabs

N.B.
	The widget files are computer-generated. The real source is
	*.w. It has been processed with Wbuild (available by
	anonymous ftp from ftp.let.rug.nl)

Author
	Bert Bos <bert@let.rug.nl>
	Alfa-informatica, Rijksuniversiteit Groningen, The Netherlands
	July 1994

	rotated.c & rotated.h are copyright Alan Richardson
	(mppa3@syma.sussex.ac.uk), see, e.g.,
	<ftp://hpux.csc.liv.ac.uk/hpux/X11/Misc/xvertext-5.0/> for the
	full package and the manuals.

History:

1.0	(29 Jul '94) first version (copied from XfwfTabs, v2.0)
1.1	(9 Feb '95) The main tab is now larger than the
	others. textMargin resource added.
2.0	(9 Jun '95) Added $orientation, $skew, $tabWidthPercentage;
	added clipping to rotated.c. Added #resize and XClearArea to
	resize.
2.1	(10 Apr '96) fixed division by zero when there is only one tab (thanks to 

